Colgate Barbie Toothbrush (Assorted) Price: Rs.69

We all know her and she has been a part of all of our childhood games and fantasies; Barbie is one of the biggest icons of timeless elegance
column13:
charm and fashion and has been around for decades. Now the beauty queen joins hands with India\u2019s popular oral care brand Colgate to create and amazing toothbrush that your little one will love. The Colgate Barbie Toothbrush has been designed for children aged 5 years and above and keeps those pearly whites shining bright.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe battery powered Barbie Toothbrush has bristles that are gentle on your child\u2019s sensitive teeth and gums. The extra soft head of the toothbrush ensures that your child is not bruised during brushing. The small head of the brush oscillates to get to every corner of the mouth to keep teeth clean. The cushioned handle of the brush is easy to grip with little fingers and makes brushing easy
